with me that day?

13
00:00:25,520 --> 00:00:27,280
Ramin, I was
your first man.

14
00:00:27,920 --> 00:00:28,880
People like me

15
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:32,440
never have the right
to control my own life.

16
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:33,800
Just once,

17
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:35,600
I wanted to
have a choice

18
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:37,200
