with them?

23
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:46,440
Yes.

24
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:49,640
It just happened
to be you that day.

25
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:58,880
So all this time,

26
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:02,040
