I used you.

30
00:01:10,440 --> 00:01:11,800
At the fencing hall

31
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,680
and at the club,

32
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:16,000
I only wanted Chai
to see that

33
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:17,640
