to deceive you.

35
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:23,880
I used my own body

36
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:25,360
as a bargaining chip.

37
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:26,480
I thought

38
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:29,520
