about it seriously?

41
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:38,600
Did you think
it was just a deal?

42
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:41,120
Did you think
everything I did for you

43
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:43,480
was business?

44
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:47,440
Do you have a heart?

45
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:55,800
You can't even look me
in the eyes.

46
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:57,240
I know

47
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,280
