49
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,400
You can't fool me.

50
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:05,720
If you want me,

51
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:08,400
I'll sleep
with you tonight.

52
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:11,840
I'll stay and serve you

53
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:14,160
until you're satisfied.

54
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,400
